  "title": "Scrub Nurse (Hospital) - Entry level [GC]",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Maintain a sterile environment in the operating theatre, ensuring all protocols are followed.</li>\n  <li>Support surgeons during procedures by handling and providing instruments and supplies.</li>\n  <li>Ensure surgical instruments and equipment are properly sterilized and prepared for use.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and assist with patient care throughout the surgical process.</li>\n  <li>Comply with strict infection control and safety guidelines.</li>\n  <li>Keep detailed and accurate records of surgical procedures and equipment utilized.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Registered Nurse with a valid license from the Singapore Nursing Board.</li>\n  <li>Training is provided.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
